36
00:01:57,430 --> 00:01:58,150
in the blink of an eye.

37
00:01:58,950 --> 00:01:59,560
Tell me about it.

38
00:02:01,070 --> 00:02:02,640
I went to all the shops in the city.

39
00:02:03,000 --> 00:02:03,590
