64
00:02:47,630 --> 00:02:48,710
I have no idea

65
00:02:48,840 --> 00:02:49,520
why Miss Hua invited us.

66
00:02:51,360 --> 00:02:51,910
Let's go.

67
00:02:52,960 --> 00:02:53,590
Gentlemen,

68
00:02:53,630 --> 00:02:54,680
