226
00:07:48,430 --> 00:07:49,120
Let me go, please!

227
00:07:50,120 --> 00:07:50,600
Good!

228
00:07:51,560 --> 00:07:52,070
Good!

229
00:07:53,070 --> 00:07:54,040
That man indeed deserves to die.

230
00:07:59,310 --> 00:08:00,600
